summary: Will you get round to answering all your complex asks backlog once you're feeling better? Obviously feel free to ignore any of...
question: Will you get round to answering all your complex asks backlog once you're feeling better? Obviously feel free to ignore any of the Ethan Wacker ones ROFL
answer:
Yeah! I answer almost everything people send me. Sometimes it takes me a few days to find the right way to word some of my more complex answers so it will spend a few days in my drafts. 

I have probably 50 unanswered asks from the last 24 hours though and even though they aren’t all complex, the sheer volume can be overwhelming sometimes so I’m just taking my time with them. 

The last four or five days on here have just been a bit exhausting between the dumb Wuffy drama and what happened with Josh. It kind of messed with my mental health a bit esp last night so I’m just taking things slow and keeping it light for now!! But I should get around to answering most of the asks this week.  I’ll probably answer some of them when I get bored enough in the middle of the night tonight.

summary: TJ: Hey Jonah, do you think you can help me sing a song for Cyrus? And by "help me sing", I really mean sing the whole song for...
body:
TJ: Hey Jonah, do you think you can help me sing a song for Cyrus? And by “help me sing”, I really mean sing the whole song for me while I play the piano? Cuz I can’t actually sing?

Jonah: Wait, you want me to … serenade Cyrus?

TJ: Well not exactly, just help me serenade him. Since you can sing and all.

Jonah: Why can’t you serenade him yourself?

TJ: Cuz … I can’t sing. Which I kinda just said.

Jonah: Well then you should find somebody who can!

TJ: I- I literally just did!

Jonah: Really? That’s great! Who??

TJ: *buries face into hands*
